<div class="post"><div class="posttop"><div class="username">Aennyil</div><div class="date">December 13th, 2004, 12:08 PM</div></div><div class="posttext">Doesn't sound like a whole lot that a consumer attorney can do for you aside from run you up another bill. One wonders how accurate these schmendricks are though when they report their income to the IRS.  :evil: <br />
